% Facts: symptoms of diseases
disease(flu) :- symptom(fever), symptom(cough), symptom(headache).
disease(cold) :- symptom(sneezing), symptom(cough), symptom(runny_nose).
disease(malaria) :- symptom(fever), symptom(chills), symptom(sweating).
disease(typhoid) :- symptom(fever), symptom(abdominal_pain), symptom(headache).

